title: Iclone.Library.2015.Content.Collection.-manaze
description:
/////////////////////////////
--------------------------------------------------------
OFFICIAL Iclone Library 2015(Content.Collection)-manaze

Note: This Update will require 50Gigs of Hard-Drive Space.

-Welcome to the long awaited expansion pack for iclone V4.x V5.x v6.x
I have TESTED the expansion only with Iclone5.5 and prior.

Note: Iclone 6 is the next level in animation,
and I strongly suggest purchasing the product.

No full version's of iclone are included in this release,
only content for users to enjoy the program with.


This Expansion will update all section's of iclone.
--------------------------------------------------------

Install:  
-Locate your iclone template folder: 

C:UsersPublicDocumentsReallusionTemplateiClone 5 Template

Merge my iclone template folder with yours by selecting 
and copy pasting into the same directory.  

Answer any windows prompts and click yes for merge. 
Keep file name's that are different sizes with same name,
they may be different.

Please seed this for a long, long time. 

Enjoy
-Manaze

PS: I included a Movie I made that took 4 years to complete. 
It shows the various stages I was at animating, and how
I got better towards the end.

It includes 4 different raves, and 8 Episodes.

Inside The Mind Of Manaze
